Viz.js Distribution — Third-Party Notices
==========================================

This vendored bundle is `viz-standalone.js` from the npm package
`@viz-js/viz` v3.26.0 (https://github.com/mdaines/viz-js). The file
contains three distinct bodies of code combined into a single script:
the Viz.js JavaScript wrapper, the Graphviz graph-layout library
(compiled to WebAssembly), and the Expat XML parser (compiled to
WebAssembly). Each is distributed under its own license. All three
licenses apply to this file.

